descriptionHtml:
Second texture mod, this time I increased the resolution of the female Female Elven Cuirass (Main part of armor) from 1024x1024 to 2048x2048. I left the normal maps to the original size since I\'m not great with normal\'s. 

I also made it a bit more colorful as it was a bit washed out on the original.

I\'ll be updating the full suit tomorrow but for now its just the main part.

Made for myself and practice but want to share with others.
Have fun!
author: kokamoo
